Hi all. 

Update: Fixed alot of problems in this version, including game killing bug that people can abuse, and also a massive bug with cubemaps.

Here my newest map, its pritty small but then agean so is sorrento. Been doing alot of testing so this version should be fine for all.

Key Points

.Good spawn. 'same one seen in my other maps'

.Easy maze.

.No pointless runing 'meaning every time you run, you have the chance of having zombies right behind.

.Semi Large defending stage, where people need to defend a small fort.

.Climbing stage, not every one is going to make it to the top in time. But this makes it even better when you get to the top and live.

.New art style.

'warning this map is stronge on hdr'

Also dont resubmit my work, or send my drunk friends after you!
